nodes.text: Jyml was a male individual who resided in the Damotite mining village on the Outer Rim planet Lanteeb during the waning years of the Galactic Republic. On one occasion, Jyml lost several toes while working in the village's mine, despite wearing protective boots at the time. Jyml later died of old age at some point prior to the liberation of Lanteeb during the Clone Wars.
